# Parent  5b33b070378ae0806bed0b5e5e34de429a29e7db
Bug 1420229 - Create a new components.css file and load it as a UA stylesheet

This provides a place for XBL stylesheets to exist with less important application
than a document sheet, similar to the presentation hint that they currently have

MozReview-Commit-ID: 3ewomJZMbrk

